      <h1>2021-12-06 || Ornament Factory</h1>
      <p>This holly day you will make an app where you can make your own ornament, using a graphics framework Raylib.</p>
      <p>Suggestions: Export the ornament as an image, more decorations, make it into a 3D model then export it as obj, so you can 3D print it.</p>
      <h2>RESTRICTIONS</h2>
      <p>You have to make it using Raylib.</p>
      <p>Don't copy some code, and try making it unique.</p>
      <p>Use C# or ReCT to code this exercise, but C and Lua is also allowed, if you really want to.</p>
      <h3>EXAMPLES</h3>
